Of course, bro! Here's the same cute webpage in English, made to impress that sweet girl:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>For Someone Special</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffc0cb, #ffe4e1);
      font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px;
      color: #d6336c;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 0.2em;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .heart {
      font-size: 5em;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); }
    }
    .note {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #6a1b4d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="heart">❤️</div>
  <h1>Hey Beautiful Girl!</h1>
  <p>You’re not just beautiful… you’re pure magic!</p>
